import { Component, Inject } from '@angular/core'; import { HttpClient } from '@angular/common/http'; @Component({ selector: 'app-fetch-data', templateUrl: './fetch-data.component.html' }) export class FetchDataComponent { public fx: Effects[] = []; ; constructor(http: HttpClient, @Inject('BASE_URL') baseUrl: string) { http.get(baseUrl + 'effects').subscribe(result => { this.fx = [result]; }, error => console.error(error)); } } interface Effects { username: string; effects: string[]; }
